            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>1. 外資累計賣超 5 日的股票<br/>凱基金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2883:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2883\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2883-TW</a>)、元大金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2885:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2885\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2885-TW</a>)、台新金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2887:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2887\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2887-TW</a>)、群創 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3481:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3481\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3481-TW</a>)、台積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2330-TW</a>)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>2. 外資累計賣超 4 日的股票<br/>凱基金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2883:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2883\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2883-TW</a>)、群創 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3481:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3481\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3481-TW</a>)、台